

<view class="cu-card dynamic {{isCard?'no-card':''}}">
  <view class="cu-item shadow">
    <view class="cu-list menu-avatar">
      <view class="cu-item">
        <view class="cu-avatar round lg" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10006.jpg);"></view>
        <view class="content flex-sub">
          <view>凯尔</view>
          <view class="text-gray text-sm flex justify-between">
            2019年12月3日
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="text-content">
      折磨生出苦难，苦难又会加剧折磨，凡间这无穷的循环，将有我来终结！
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="cu-card article">
  <view class="cu-item shadow">
    <view class="title">
      <view class="cuIcon-playfill text-green play"></view>
      <view class="cu-progress round xs striped active progress">
        <view class="bg-orange" style="width:60%"></view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="content">
      <view class="grid col-2 margin-bottom text-center">
        <view class="text-lg text-green padding-xs answer">{{question.dialect}}</view>
        <block wx:for="{{question.wrong}}" wx:for-item="wrong" wx:key>
        <view class="text-df padding-xs answer">{{wrong}}</view>
        </block>
        <view class=" margin-top-xs">
          <view class="cu-tag bg-red light sm round">{{question.difficult}}</view>
          <view class="cu-tag bg-green light sm round">{{question.district}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="bg-green light padding-xs margin-xs text-center round shadow shadow-warp btn" bindtap="toDetail">编辑</view>
  </view>
</view>